data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning property features 3 bedrooms plus a den, 2 bathrooms, and a beautiful outdoor pool and is located in the desirable Canyon Trails neighborhood. The leased solar system, fully paid off until 2032, ensures low utility bills. This home is move in ready and boasts tile flooring throughout the home, modern light fixtures, and an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The home also offers a water filtration system. Outside you'll find 3 fruit trees, an RV Gate, an irrigation system in the front and backyard, and a sparkling pool with a motorized retractable shade. This home offers not only comfort and style but also a prime location, less than 5 minutes to Target and Fry's. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your forever home!
